Class CandidateMappingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.krr.logmap2.mappings.MappingManager
      • uk.ac.ox.krr.logmap2.mappings.CandidateMappingManager

  • public class CandidateMappingManager
extends MappingManager
    This class extracts the anchors by intersecting the lexical inverted files associated with the respective ontologies. It will also manage the discovery of further mappings

    Ernesto Jimenez-Ruiz Created: Dec 13, 2011
